  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Cut the <strong>potatoes </strong>(skins on) into chips and add them to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p><p>Season with a generous grind of<strong> black pepper </strong>and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Put the tray in the oven for 30 min or until golden and crisp – these are your<strong> black pepper chips</strong></p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1618244435507-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1618244435507-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1618244435507-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1618244435507-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1618244435507-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the chips are cooking, chop the<strong> tomato<span class=\"text-danger\">[es]</strong> </span>roughly</p><p>Heat a pot with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped tomatoes</strong> with the<strong> smoked paprika </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and cook for 2-3 min</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1618244467373-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1618244467373-x400.jpg",
