      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Remove 2 <span class=\"text-danger\">[4]</span> <strong>outer leaves</strong> from the<strong> gem lettuce</strong> and set aside for serving</p><p>Chop the <strong>remaining lettuce</strong> into wedges</p><p>Combine the<strong> cider vinegar </strong>with 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil </strong>– this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
