    {
      "instruction": "<p>Slice the <strong>ciabattas</strong> in half</p><p>Once the chips have been cooking for 20 min, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> meat-free bacon rashers</strong> and cook for 3 min on each side or until golden and crisp</p><p>Once done, transfer to a plate and reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 5,
